@page "/spinners"
<h3>Spinner Component</h3>
<p>A spinner alerts a user that content is being loaded or processed, and they should wait for the activity to complete.</p>
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="p-2 interactivity-card">
        <h5>Parameters</h5>
        <table class="table table-sm mb-0">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_color" style="margin-right: 5px;">Color</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" id="option_color" style="width: 150px;" @bind-value=_interactiveColor></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_secondary_color" style="margin-right: 5px;">Secondary Color</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" id="option_secondary_color" style="width: 150px;" @bind-value=_interactivesSecondaryColor></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_label" style="margin-right: 5px;">Label</label></td>
                    <td><input type="text" id="option_label" style="width: 150px;" @bind-value=_interactiveLabel></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_label_placement" style="margin-right: 5px;">Label Placement</label></td>
                    <td>
                        <select id="option_label_placement" @bind-value=_interactiveLabelPlacement @bind-value:event="onchange">
                            <option value=@Placement.Top>Top</option>
                            <option value=@Placement.Left>Left</option>
                            <option value=@Placement.Bottom selected>Bottom</option>
                            <option value=@Placement.Right>Right</option>
                        </select>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_type" style="margin-right: 5px;">Type</label></td>
                    <td>
                        <select id="option_type" @bind-value=_interactiveType @bind-value:event="onchange">
                            <option value=@SpinType.Blocks>Blocks</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Circle>Circle</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.DualRing>Dual Ring</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Ellipsis>Ellipsis</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Hourglass>Hourglass</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Pulse>Pulse</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Ring selected>Ring</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Roller>Roller</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.SpinIOS>Spin iOS</option>
                            <option value=@SpinType.Square>Square</option>
                        </select>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_size" style="margin-right: 5px;">Size</label></td>
                    <td>
                        <select id="option_size" @bind-value=_interactiveSize @bind-value:event="onchange">
                            <option value=@Size.ExtraSmall>Extra Small</option>
                            <option value=@Size.Small selected>Small</option>
                            <option value=@Size.Medium>Medium</option>
                            <option value=@Size.Large>Large</option>
                            <option value=@Size.ExtraLarge>Extra Large</option>
                        </select>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><label for="option_visible" style="margin-right: 5px;">IsVisible</label></td>
                    <td><ToggleSwitch @bind-Checked=_interactiveVisibility Label="@_toggleLabel" /></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div class="p-2 flex-grow-1 justify-content-center">
        <Spinner @bind-Color=_interactiveColor
                 @bind-SecondaryColor=_interactivesSecondaryColor
                 @bind-Label=_interactiveLabel
                 @bind-LabelPlacement=_interactiveLabelPlacement
                 @bind-Type=_interactiveType
                 @bind-Size=_interactiveSize
                 @bind-IsVisible=_interactiveVisibility
                 />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Default Spinner</h4>
<p>This is a spinner with the default properties and styles.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner />
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Label (optional)</h4>
<p>The spinner component can also display an optional label if it is provided as a parameter.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Label="Loading..." /&gt;</code></pre>
<div style="width: 56px">
    <Spinner Label="Loading..." />
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With LabelPlacement</h4>
<p>The spinner component allows you to place the label in four different positions:</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Label="Top..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Top /&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Top..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Top />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Bottom..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Bottom />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Left..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Left />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Right..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Right />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner Visibility</h4>
<p>This is a spinner that allows changing of the IsVisible property to show and hide the spinner.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner IsVisible=@this._spinnerVisible /&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" @onclick="ToggleSpinnerVisibility">
            Toggle Visibility
        </button>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner IsVisible=@this._spinnerVisible />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Color Parameters</h4>
<p>The spinner component also allows for simple customizations via component parameter: Color and SecondaryColor.
   Color is the spinner's foreground color. 
   SecondaryColor is only supported for a few spinners (Ring, DualRing, and Hourglass) to allow a background color change.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Type=SpinType.DualRing Color="green" SecondaryColor="yellow" /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner Type=SpinType.DualRing Color="green" SecondaryColor="yellow" />
<hr />

